### EduPortal API - Schedules Controller
### Lesson schedule management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/schedules
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL SCHEDULES - Paginated list (Admin only)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SCHEDULE BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SCHEDULES BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SCHEDULES BY TEACHER
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/teacher/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE SCHEDULE - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "courseId": 1,
  "teacherId": 1,
  "classId": 1,
  "classroomId": 1,
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "09:45:00",
  "academicYear": "2024-2025",
  "semester": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE SCHEDULE - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "10:45:00",
  "classroomId": 2,
  "isActive": true
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE SCHEDULE - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
